INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4986,'Shutter','Shutter','allotracker','','Shutter is a 2008 American remake of the 2004 Thai horror film of the same name. The remake was directed by Masayuki Ochiai, and was released on March 21, 2008.
INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4987,'The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover','The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover','allotracker','','The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover is a 1989 French/British romantic crime drama written and directed by Peter Greenaway, starring Richard Bohringer, Michael Gambon, Helen Mirren, and Alan Howard in the titular roles. The film''s graphic scatological, violent and nude scenes, as well as its lavish cinematography and formalism were noted at the time of its release.
INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4988,'Coffee and Cigarettes','Coffee and Cigarettes','allotracker','','Coffee and Cigarettes is the title of three short films and a 2003 feature film by independent director Jim Jarmusch. The 2003 film consists of 11 short stories which share coffee and cigarettes as a common thread, and includes the earlier three films.
INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4989,'Festen','The Celebration','allotracker','','Produced by Nimbus Film, The Celebration is a 1998 Danish film by director Thomas Vinterberg, the first to be created under Dogme 95 rules. He was inspired to write it with Mogens Rukov, based on a hoax broadcast by a Danish radio station. Its original Danish title is Festen, and it was released under this title in the UK. The film tells the story of a family gathering to celebrate their father''s 60th birthday. At the dinner, the eldest son publicly accuses his father of sexually abusing both him and his twin sister (who had recently committed suicide).
INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4990,'Julia''s eyes','Julia''s Eyes','allotracker','','Julia''s Eyes (Spanish: Los ojos de Julia) is a 2010 Spanish horror-thriller film directed by Guillem Morales and written by Morales and Oriol Paulo.
INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4991,'The tortured','Tortured','allotracker','','Tortured is a 2008 crime thriller film written and directed by Nolan Lebovitz and starring Cole Hauser, Laurence Fishburne, and James Cromwell. It was released direct-to-DVD in the U.S. on September 16, 2008. The movie was filmed in Canada, in Vancouver, British Columbia.
INSERT INTO "movies" VALUES(4992,'Ces amours là','What Love May Bring','allotracker','','Ces amours-là is a 2010 French film directed by Claude Lelouch.
